        "subject": "LU-1187 osd: Do not add remote fid to idmap cache.",
        "message": "LU-1187 osd: Do not add remote fid to idmap cache.\n\nOI cache suppose only includes <local fid, local ino>, if we add\n<remote_fid, agent ino> to the cache, it might confuse osd in some\ncases, i.e. get an object through oi_lookup by a remote fid.\n\nSigned-off-by: Wang Di <di.wang@whamcloud.com>\nChange-Id: I6414188aab2b6c10a41c22742291521d97a4a171\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
  },
